{"tid":115864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滅火筒常識","createTime":"2017-02-11T01:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T02:43:24.000Z","uid":44562,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1eea0a8173f89e23ee870c8017239b6710f4ccab","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"滅火筒基本上都是按火的種類分為5類<br />\nA 含碳可燃固體之火警，如木、草、紙張、塑膠、橡膠<br />\nB 可燃液體之火警，如汽油、柴油、油、機油<br />\nC 可燃氣體之火警，如石油氣、天然氣、乙炔、甲烷<br />\nD 可燃固體金屬之火警，如鎂、銅、鐵、鋁、鈉、鉀、鋰<br />\nE 通電物體之火警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵在車廂內裝置的是乾粉筒<br />\n粉劑滅火筒，即是乾粉筒，可撲滅各類別的火警，故名為&quot;ABC&quot;型。不過乾粉用在撲滅電子設備發生的火，事後清理就好麻煩，亦會對電子設備構成破壞，所以用就算滅了火，那些電子設備多數要報銷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯請補充~ 謝謝~"},{"pid":"ee26cdaf3ef6dbf9d0d09a5e329257812dde84fb","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"如何使用乾粉滅火筒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cYo_6L2zByo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcYo_6L2zByo&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f7e38330\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cYo_6L2zByo</a>"},{"pid":"346c2259ea53bcabfff22bcce1dd5515e3c4653f","tid":115864,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用"},{"pid":"64aa463c373959f31a5fd10d3bc5937d2f4d118d","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用</blockquote><br />\nthanks!"},{"pid":"ab39b57a9ce7b55869a05504ff8114a7490fc875","tid":115864,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"地鐵車廂已經放左啱用嘅滅火筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e2f7b7bdd8c0e78d31ef61a3931ff0f6bd34e4","tid":115864,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正確做法係睇噴咀"},{"pid":"a146a4068749aa521b542b1ffc7e2bd3a7e7b461","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵車廂已經放左啱用嘅滅火筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好易用, 但無人試 ...."},{"pid":"566b4cec7eef7133cce65c3930f28ddd6b0f4832","tid":115864,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5175adc24e3dba998c8121eb355037a5ac9b85","tid":115864,"uid":61278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上"},{"pid":"eb4ca3e428d84e94c365084fead578b20922d4b7","tid":115864,"uid":35021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰"},{"pid":"38697a5636c4e2c613635a0b588d27111e08a288","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?"},{"pid":"47a726d9bb4ec801d80d1bcb5d26066fa64a8ae5","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"&bull; 噴出的乾粉會減低能見度，令人難以辨別方向<br />\n&bull; 使用時切勿手持噴咀，以免凍傷"},{"pid":"26f4cca5a9f816d6a4c07207a19f9eb00fd9bd42","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"找到了些資料~<br />\n<br />\n乾粉滅火器不能往人身上噴, 可能會令傷者窒息, 也容易使燒傷創面感染細菌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fsociety%2Fg496r9.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8934bd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html</a>"},{"pid":"655a68a3f71c2f594ef81c01ccd98dfab615335a","tid":115864,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&bull; 噴出的乾粉會減低能見度，令人難以辨別方向<br />\n&bull; 使用時切勿手持噴咀，以免凍傷</blockquote><br />\n咁我覺得封閉車廂入面唔好噴會好啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7304afadef3e960a1c2ee7c59d9d42f7ecff9a74","tid":115864,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9708b3aef0e0ece5915b6461258abb0f65f9b1e","tid":115864,"uid":2277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一出fm200 單野就唔係叫意外 叫慘劇啦"},{"pid":"7026e78168b686709bcd0c5b11da1fc1b4b8a062","tid":115864,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFm 200 用係有人既地方架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果成個站都係fm200 就成月台人死曬啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb1cba3b9f64d6560e445db54703037ca7a0191","tid":115864,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFm 200 用係有人既地方架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果成個站都係fm200 就成月台人死曬啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFM200 (CF3CHFCF3---七氟丙烷) 氣體是一種化合物，由碳、氟及氫組成。它無色，無味，不導電，易揮發的氣體。並通過中斷燃燒過程以及改變區域內氧氣含量來達到滅火效果。當在封閉區域內使用時，濃度等級應小於等於對人體無害的濃度。所以系統設計為10秒鐘之內氣體噴入被保護區域，達到最小滅火濃度為 7.44 % (UL) 或 7 % (FM)，但不能超過 9 %。氣體滅火濃度要參照所在區域的最低環境溫度。<br />\n所以當計算滅火濃度時，必須確定最高環境溫度下，被保護區域內濃度不超過NFPA2001規定之9%的對人體無害的濃度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現時香港所採用的濃度，一般不會多於 7.xx%。因此，即使噴氣後而沒有抽氣系統，也不𥅽在對人體有害。<br />\n濃度等級\t  暴露時間限制<br />\n9%或以下 (對人體無害濃度) (NOAEL)\t   無限制<br />\n9%以上至10.5%\t 1分鐘以內<br />\n大於10.5% 不能有任何接觸</span><br />\n<br />\n不過通常都等無人先會放氣"},{"pid":"80b85258aff66f8e2936ff2dd0dcda00d1ef475e","tid":115864,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFm 200 用係有人既地方架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果成個站都係fm200 就成月台人死曬啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFM200 (CF3CHFCF3---七氟丙烷) 氣體是一種化合物，由碳、氟及氫組成。它無色，無味，不導電，易揮發的氣體。並通過中斷燃燒過程以及改變區域內氧氣含量來達到滅火效果。當在封閉區域內使用時，濃度等級應小於等於對人體無害的濃度。所以系統設計為10秒鐘之內氣體噴入被保護區域，達到最小滅火濃度為 7.44 % (UL) 或 7 % (FM)，但不能超過 9 %。氣體滅火濃度要參照所在區域的最低環境溫度。<br />\n所以當計算滅火濃度時，必須確定最高環境溫度下，被保護區域內濃度不超過NFPA2001規定之9%的對人體無害的濃度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現時香港所採用的濃度，一般不會多於 7.xx%。因此，即使噴氣後而沒有抽氣系統，也不𥅽在對人體有害。<br />\n濃度等級\t  暴露時間限制<br />\n9%或以下 (對人體無害濃度) (NOAEL)\t   無限制<br />\n9%以上至10.5%\t 1分鐘以內<br />\n大於10.5% 不能有任何接觸</span><br />\n<br />\n不過通常都等無人先會放氣</blockquote><br />\nFm200要密室先有用，有人就要開抽風，即係無鳩用<br />\n吸入對人體無害，但個人係無抽風系統下，太多FM200會谷走晒D氧氣窒息死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f690de83759ca9929c1461805ec4e0619748cf3","tid":115864,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你"},{"pid":"1483d37826ebd04336d2ea8e2b6942b9e0f7fedf","tid":115864,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.safetypostershop.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/fire-extinguisher-AUS-classification.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.safetypostershop.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2Ffire-extinguisher-AUS-classification.jpg&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2f2097d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.safetypostershop.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/fire-extinguisher-AUS-classification.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"d1267778b6911cd32ab61d57ea59cc80a6364dfd","tid":115864,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地鐵站唔係有fm200 架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒到咁都唔著alarm 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFm 200 用係有人既地方架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果成個站都係fm200 就成月台人死曬啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFM200 (CF3CHFCF3---七氟丙烷) 氣體是一種化合物，由碳、氟及氫組成。它無色，無味，不導電，易揮發的氣體。並通過中斷燃燒過程以及改變區域內氧氣含量來達到滅火效果。當在封閉區域內使用時，濃度等級應小於等於對人體無害的濃度。所以系統設計為10秒鐘之內氣體噴入被保護區域，達到最小滅火濃度為 7.44 % (UL) 或 7 % (FM)，但不能超過 9 %。氣體滅火濃度要參照所在區域的最低環境溫度。<br />\n所以當計算滅火濃度時，必須確定最高環境溫度下，被保護區域內濃度不超過NFPA2001規定之9%的對人體無害的濃度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現時香港所採用的濃度，一般不會多於 7.xx%。因此，即使噴氣後而沒有抽氣系統，也不𥅽在對人體有害。<br />\n濃度等級\t  暴露時間限制<br />\n9%或以下 (對人體無害濃度) (NOAEL)\t   無限制<br />\n9%以上至10.5%\t 1分鐘以內<br />\n大於10.5% 不能有任何接觸</span><br />\n<br />\n不過通常都等無人先會放氣</blockquote><br />\nFm200唔係直接對人體有害, 而係令人無曬氧氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d7b2fffd767a97eadd1a1f7ccb958b7808b000","tid":115864,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正確做法係睇噴咀</blockquote><br />\n普通人邊識咁多，試一下先噴係最直接簡單一般人都做得到"},{"pid":"1f5952054d8f6595e31bfa3b99bcbecc49d4d412","tid":115864,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"聽上面班戇鳩講fm200 真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"a67fbcd03060ab7cc881b24c0b7a4fa3376ec5c5","tid":115864,"uid":83647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8192a3e400e8734b87de672dc1d2211d5561881c","tid":115864,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9035f9c455eecd8c7888dd60f1afd88ada2b75","tid":115864,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正確做法係睇噴咀</blockquote><br />\n普通人邊識咁多，試一下先噴係最直接簡單一般人都做得到</blockquote><br />\n依家新的滅火筒全部統一曬做紅色，要知係乜要睇lable，因為以前好多on9以為滅火筒一定係紅色，其他顏色唔知係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059edfddfb3345dd56968967369ac9320c32ad31","tid":115864,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b151a35836e2d980b5a0dd8e17adc34b55585c03","tid":115864,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"地鐵個支係藍色？"},{"pid":"9a5429df7bb709d9303fd05e5063061aef85c589","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵個支係藍色？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"a7aef73611249a1ac76606529f5f460f0c2a1992","tid":115864,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地鐵個支係藍色？</blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/161657_683e7d6fd71347f173ef8933239a139b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F161657_683e7d6fd71347f173ef8933239a139b.jpg&h=9275669d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 係街 upload , 要側下頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42edda3bb5068bee5e20354cd43826089860f610","tid":115864,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指正"},{"pid":"71a64fb30efc93c247cd3ed46626a906bcad75dd","tid":115864,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用滅火氈，冇就係地下翻滾<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有過期海上救火牌同急救牌"},{"pid":"7fd7a261e4ff23f723b4dfc934437e39a540a01b","tid":115864,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有唔好信d color code,  向冇人地方噴一噴confirm咩劑先用</blockquote><br />\nthanks!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過救火果陣個滅火筒唔出野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb410ae6fc43b2c7de0462c4ab845da45550f687","tid":115864,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n咁由佢繼續燒吧白痴"},{"pid":"5e010943c658d0f01b4f70043c2b85430ab64e83","tid":115864,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>找到了些資料~<br />\n<br />\n乾粉滅火器不能往人身上噴, 可能會令傷者窒息, 也容易使燒傷創面感染細菌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fsociety%2Fg496r9.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8934bd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦，咁由佢繼續燒吧"},{"pid":"1770a1433faf9e79e275bcd81c090fcf5819e411","tid":115864,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n冇正規救火知識既人想救火，第一時間係諗有冇水，之後係諗滅火筒，乜都冇先會諗用野拍熄<br />\n講咩要睇 d 火係咩類型火，咩類烈滅火筒，拍火既野係咩物料易唔易然<br />\n慢慢分析條友都燒撚熟左<br />\n佢地點解咁諗就想話比人知自己有救火知識，但唔係常識<br />\n咩未燒到皮仲好笑，有條友著左火仲觀察人燒到幾成熟都唔救左火先<br />\n事後感染已經唔係第一考慮點"},{"pid":"bf84a121b866c4cc693426c0bf125e19c9d5c360","tid":115864,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n冇正規救火知識既人想救火，第一時間係諗有冇水，之後係諗滅火筒，乜都冇先會諗用野拍熄<br />\n講咩要睇 d 火係咩類型火，咩類烈滅火筒，拍火既野係咩物料易唔易然<br />\n慢慢分析條友都燒撚熟左<br />\n佢地點解咁諗就想話比人知自己有救火知識，但唔係常識<br />\n咩未燒到皮仲好笑，有條友著左火仲觀察人燒到幾成熟都唔救左火先<br />\n事後感染已經唔係第一考慮點</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20150629%2F638153%2F&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5a449542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/</a>"},{"pid":"b0cbc153164cca2898fecc551d60b4bbe3c671a5","tid":115864,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n冇正規救火知識既人想救火，第一時間係諗有冇水，之後係諗滅火筒，乜都冇先會諗用野拍熄<br />\n講咩要睇 d 火係咩類型火，咩類烈滅火筒，拍火既野係咩物料易唔易然<br />\n慢慢分析條友都燒撚熟左<br />\n佢地點解咁諗就想話比人知自己有救火知識，但唔係常識<br />\n咩未燒到皮仲好笑，有條友著左火仲觀察人燒到幾成熟都唔救左火先<br />\n事後感染已經唔係第一考慮點</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20150629%2F638153%2F&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5a449542\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/</a></blockquote><br />\n都係事後感染啫"},{"pid":"d8fcda6d23180489c4c52c3492a49f2e43b6e20c","tid":115864,"uid":62443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"個火人想衝向你求救咪勁噴囉，喺地下典下典下就用衫幫佢拍，邊駛睇標籤，睇自身安全。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9022b2b2b7025a61526dbad7a4bd423baa52685","tid":115864,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n冇正規救火知識既人想救火，第一時間係諗有冇水，之後係諗滅火筒，乜都冇先會諗用野拍熄<br />\n講咩要睇 d 火係咩類型火，咩類烈滅火筒，拍火既野係咩物料易唔易然<br />\n慢慢分析條友都燒撚熟左<br />\n佢地點解咁諗就想話比人知自己有救火知識，但唔係常識<br />\n咩未燒到皮仲好笑，有條友著左火仲觀察人燒到幾成熟都唔救左火先<br />\n事後感染已經唔係第一考慮點</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20150629%2F638153%2F&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5a449542\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150629/638153/</a></blockquote><br />\n都係事後感染啫</blockquote><br />\n都燒撚死左，重有咩可以感染？"},{"pid":"b0882c80e6c6160e2651a59df466522933e0e7f2","tid":115864,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n未燒到皮就得<br />\n已經燒傷就噴咗仲衰</blockquote><br />\n由佢燒會好啲 ?</blockquote><br />\n呢 d 問題佢地係唔會答你</blockquote><br />\n應該嘗試搵其他方法滅火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如用麻布等物料掩住火源隔絕氧氣嚟滅火<img sr