":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T19:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>找到了些資料~<br />\n<br />\n乾粉滅火器不能往人身上噴, 可能會令傷者窒息, 也容易使燒傷創面感染細菌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fsociety%2Fg496r9.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8934bd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/society/g496r9.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哦，咁由佢繼續燒吧</blockquote><br />\n做咩啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557791cd48283891c265634a45031ef56e45240a","tid":115864,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地鐵個支係藍色？</blockquote><br />\n係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/161657_683e7d6fd71347f173ef8933239a139b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F161657_683e7d6fd71347f173ef8933239a139b.jpg&h=9275669d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 係街 upload , 要側下頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦 圖都唔識up <br />\n仲要咁多籍口</blockquote><br />\n大陸車係紅色，但都係粉"},{"pid":"6258338e761be51eea876514a924ccb16e7c342b","tid":115864,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:59:45.000Z","msg":"講咁撚多做乜柒<br />\n反正你都係走先嗰位架啦<br />\n噴唔噴落人身上都唔識答<br />\n大佬呀佢雙腳着火咋又唔係上身着火你驚乜春<br />\n係人都會噴落去啦仲諗會唔會傷上加傷<br />\n想佢燒到柴咁定傷多少少都唔識平均返個利害關係<br />\n你唔整熄佢隨時燒埋人到啦<br />\n你驚你到時連扣都唔識開咪仲好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd22b40bcb4aa37c5acda4bf11baf38ecb91eb4d","tid":115864,"uid":28122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T22:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無專業人士講下如果人身上衣物著火燒到皮膚可唔可以直接噴落佢身上</blockquot